{"tid":1558983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[皇軍]警方稱警員要求蹲下時市民必要做到　呼籲盡量配合","createTime":"2019-09-10T15:41:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T17:06:26.000Z","uid":58335,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6051c3ec22e2bd26ab352cc1ceb4d1f628b1de2b","tid":1558983,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:41:43.000Z","msg":"警方星期六在大埔墟港鐵站期間，用警棍打向站內的人，部分人已蹲下。被問到是否合乎最低武力指引，行動科高級警司汪威遜表示，警方使用武力時要考慮多個因素，包括要分析何時使用相應武力，以及是否需要持續使用，並非只考慮畫面當刻的情況。他不評論個別使用警棍的個案，是否合理，但表示警察使用武力的困難，在於面對的人「會郁」，會出現不同情況，當時情況混亂、充滿暴力，警方要確保安全，亦不知道他們身上會否有其他武器，因此在警員要求蹲下時，市民一定要做到，警方要絕對控制他們蹲在安全位置，否則確保不到警員或其他人不會受到傷害。他呼籲市民應盡量配合警方，警方在場作出警告及指示，是為市民好，是沒有討論空間，警方不會針對任何人，而使用武力時是有理據。警察公共關係科總警司謝振中表示，警員當日截查約10人，但並不代表當時港鐵站內只有這班人，有大批暴力示威者當時在大埔墟站大肆破壞，警方當時要追截許多人，重申警員截查時要求相關人士蹲下，但他們未有遵從，於是使用警棍，並在蹲下之後停止。<br />\n<br />\n2019-09-10 23:22:58<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1479894-20190910.htm?share=facebook\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1479894-20190910.htm%3Fshare%3Dfacebook&d=fwl9YqZIxHA797AeyThx4WzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=0463afd9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1479894-20190910.htm%3Fshare%3Dfacebook&h=60621bdb\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1479894-20190910.htm?share=facebook</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MoBsLJv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMoBsLJv.jpg&h=94e3d724&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"18af8eaf4dde6345e9a45216d307c2ca4fc59ae6","tid":1558983,"uid":264717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:42:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xNC7LH0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxNC7LH0.jpg&h=e94eaa63&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BVbwsWm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBVbwsWm.jpg&h=0fd57d81&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EYbsLH1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEYbsLH1.jpg&h=15b9c36a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c7f372920b8e22ded5e6739d1254bf979ad62a95","tid":1558983,"uid":69159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:43:00.000Z","msg":"沒有討論空間<br />\n有無軍禮教學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8549a40d5ef91f789582163434dfec1ffae6f8d6","tid":1558983,"uid":58335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c7f372920b8e22ded5e6739d1254bf979ad62a95","tid":1558983,"uid":69159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:43:00.000Z","msg":"沒有討論空間<br />\n有無軍禮教學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:43:36.000Z","msg":"唔知使唔使鞠躬㗎呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1e3266d27e8957c6bbb320f30a47e60202144bd","tid":1558983,"uid":91558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:45:02.000Z","msg":"[超合作運動] 全球齊篤灰 #wtsappforhk #standwithhk<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1558075\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1558075</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>拉埋外國勢力齊篤灰順便宣傳警暴</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"b98f098ce04d9a6643588ed866966f4795b5feb8","tid":1558983,"uid":69159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8549a40d5ef91f789582163434dfec1ffae6f8d6","tid":1558983,"uid":58335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c7f372920b8e22ded5e6739d1254bf979ad62a95","tid":1558983,"uid":69159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:43:00.000Z","msg":"沒有討論空間<br />\n有無軍禮教學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:43:36.000Z","msg":"唔知使唔使鞠躬㗎呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:45:14.000Z","msg":"軍禮即有關軍事活動的禮儀。王者以禮治國，使天下歸於大同，難免會遇到內部和外部的干擾，甚至兵火的威脅。《禮記?月令》記載：「以征不義，詰誅暴慢，以明好惡，順彼遠方。」禮樂與征伐，猶如車之兩輪，不可偏廢。<br />\n<br />\n而軍隊的組建、管理等，也都離不開禮的原則。例如軍隊的規模，天子為六軍，根據禮有等差的原則，諸侯的軍隊不得超過六軍，而必須與國力相稱，大國三軍，次國二軍，小國一軍。當時的軍力往往用戰車的多少來衡量，故而，又有天子萬乘，諸侯千乘，大夫百乘的說法。軍隊必須按照禮的原則，嚴格訓練，嚴格管理，《禮記?曲禮》云：「班朝治軍，蒞官行法，非禮威嚴不行。」<br />\n<br />\n軍禮分為大師之禮、大均之禮、大田之禮、大役之禮、大封之禮，《周禮&middot;春官&middot;大宗伯》記載：「大師之禮，用眾也；大均之禮，恤眾也；大田之禮，簡眾也；大役之禮，任眾也；大封之禮，合眾也。」包括用兵征伐，均土地和征賦稅，田獵，營建土木工程，定疆封土等活動中的禮儀。"},{"pid":"99d69fcbed06687478f9e7ce46fc12b8102dd9b5","tid":1558983,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:47:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd00e5a64384be2350133d23ee3c7b0e0f4ee905","tid":1558983,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:48:48.000Z","msg":"行納粹禮係咪唔使比黑警打"},{"pid":"0751527f1f13e53b095b5efabd1211050446ed29","tid":1558983,"uid":83990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:49:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />dllm"},{"pid":"d7a0c189d96b5feaa4c48bc6e407775b1308e6d6","tid":1558983,"uid":260271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:49:23.000Z","msg":"警察使用武力的困難，在於面對的人「會郁」<br />\n所以首先就打到佢地唔識郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後唔遵從你又可以打<br />\n不如你講下咩情況下係唔打好撚過啦皇軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce4e4538afd323588d23cf66bca5c8316cc9a8df","tid":1558983,"uid":58335